{
  "stem": "7455.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from a distance, they noticed two bodies, two boys walking at the edge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the boys ran in, it was suspicious to them, because they saw them from a distance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans got off their motorcycles, and they had machine guns, and went into the woods to search-- to get them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those boys had weapons, because they hoped to join the partisan group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had some guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were hiding in the woods and running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans found them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The boys were starting to shoot-- didn't aim-- and the Germans apprehended them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They left their motorcycles-- nobody's going to steal them, a German motorcycle-- and they walked, because it was near the town, walked them under-- under guard, to the Ukrainian kommandantur.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Ukrainians were helping-- they were the militia-- to bring them there, feeling they're going to take care of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they brought them to that Ukrainian militia, and they left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Ukrainians were-- knew that they're Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They're going to send them out, and somebody who does that function will shoot them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while the boys were leaving and crying, begging, the Ukrainians said, you have a good pair of boots-- those high boots.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You don't need them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Where you're going, you don't need them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Take them off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the boy-- the boots are very heavy, hard to remove.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was struggling, putting down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody is looking at him, what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, this German who was giving the order-- this Ukrainian, I mean, who was telling him, give me the boots, on the desk there was a gun.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As the boy was taking off the boots, he noticed the gun on the edge of the desk.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
